We consider a magnetic SkX on a two dimensional square lattice, with its unit cell of lattice constant $2\lambda=19.8 {\mathrm \AA}$ containing $6\times 6$ spins, thus the atomic lattice spacing $a=2\lambda/6$ being 3.3\AA. 

